Decision rationale:
I rejected the Whitney compilation because, despite matching many production and vocal preferences, it is above all a greatest‑hits collection — a format I explicitly disfavor because it prioritizes singled‑out tracks over album cohesion and narrative sequencing. That format conflict is decisive: my dislike of anonymously curated hit compilations outweighs the appeal of pristine vocal production and memorable hooks in this case.
